<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>账户激活成功</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            animation: bounceIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        
        .success-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            fill: white;
        }
        
        .title {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
        }
        
        .user-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }
        
        .user-info h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .user-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .user-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .user-detail .label {
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .user-detail .value {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .actions {
            margin-top: 40px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.8s both;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e9ecef;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        
        .tips {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 1s both;
        }
        
        .tips h4 {
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .tips ul {
            text-align: left;
            color: #388e3c;
            line-height: 1.8;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 1.2s both;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.3);
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
            70% {
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 20px;
                margin: 10px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.21,11.79L9,15.58L18.79,5.79L21.21,8.21L9,20.42Z"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        
        <div class="status-badge">✅ {% if already_activated %}用户已激活{% else %}激活成功{% endif %}</div>
        
        <h1 class="title">{% if already_activated %}虽然你已经激活过啦，但还是要感谢你的支持哦~{% else %}Hi！非常感谢您的支持~{% endif %}</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            {% if already_activated %}
                您的账户已经激活过啦~
            {% else %}
                OwO欢迎加入！感谢您对我们的支持，祝您使用愉快~
            {% endif %}
        </p>
        
        <div class="user-info">
            <h3>📋 账户信息</h3>
            <div class="user-detail">
                <span class="label">用户名：</span>
                <span class="value">{{ username }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="user-detail">
                <span class="label">邮箱：</span>
                <span class="value">{{ email }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="user-detail">
                <span class="label">激活时间：</span>
                <span class="value">{{ activation_time }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="user-detail">
                <span class="label">账户状态：</span>
                <span class="value" style="color: #4CAF50;">✅ 已激活</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="tips">
            <h4>💡 使用提示</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>请妥善保管您的登录信息，避免账户信息泄露</li>
                <li>定期更新密码是保护账户安全的有效方法哦~</li>
                <li>在个人中心去完善关于您的更多信息吧！</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>🔒 保护您的账户安全就是我们的一贯使命</p>
            <p>如果您没有进行此操作，请立即联系我们</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 页面加载完成后的欢迎提示
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
            console.log('🎉 欢迎加入我们的平台！');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
